FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS What are your holiday hours? Thanksgiving – Closed Christmas Eve – Closing 1 hour early Christmas – Closed New Year’s Eve – Open normal hours New Year’s Day – Open normal hours Do You Offer Franchise Options? We do not currently offer franchise options. Do You Take Reservations? Unfortunately, due to the nature of our stores, we do not offer reservations. However, we do try our best to accommodate every guest and every request. Please reach out to your local Community Store directly to see if they are able to make something happen! Can I Order Your Coffee Online? YES!! We do sell our coffee online on our store page. Do you offer gluten free options? While our menu offers gluten friendly items (Frittaffles, Bluegrass Grits Bowl, Potatoes O'Ryan), due to the open layout of our scratch kitchens, we can't guarantee no cross contamination.
